"uid":324193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T13:32:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7d6d802f4e4c2d3b4fe3872abd0268c7e20a34e","tid":1966858,"uid":324193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T13:35:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb12f867fe10ca5114a2d9565c911f81aff2e455","tid":1966858,"uid":324193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T14:04:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />推唔到"},{"pid":"7149cb8e50eef6ffe771c81cf55319e46605fb7f","tid":1966858,"uid":324193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T16:05:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wahyj4u.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fwahyj4u.png&h=8e7d4a8b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/3egzWfh\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F3egzWfh&d=GkP5J4C4AUyWsqXHyTPi6zFPTz8k007NAABMmnbcnzw%3D&h=401fd350\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/3egzWfh</a><br />\n<br />\n（獨媒特約報導）立法會選舉將於今年9月舉行，民間集會團隊發言人劉頴匡今日於沙田站出口設置街站，呼籲選民登記，並派發宣傳初選方案的單張。劉頴匡指初選可減少民主派出選數目，繼而增加立法會民主派議席過半的機會，並直言有意參加初選。11名沙田區議員撐場支持，沙田區政區議員趙柱幫表示相信劉能把街頭抗爭的聲音帶進議會，並助民主派發動議會「全面不合作」策略。"},{"pid":"c383b7fd182350ffac5086da6d29f39d45b2c30c","tid":1966858,"uid":324193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T16:08:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"af2ff38028e1e5768ee97b7e49e5c6100575aa89","tid":1966858,"uid":324193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T16:23:27.000Z","msg":"（警世）立會選戰需要36素人Plan B<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1991695\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1991695</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}